---
import Layout from '../components/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Cookie Policy — missionctl"
  description="Cookie policy for missionctl.sh. We use only essential cookies. No tracking or advertising cookies."
>
  <article style="max-width: 760px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 5rem 1.5rem;">
    <header style="margin-bottom: 3rem;">
      <div style="font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace; font-size: 0.75rem; color: #00d97e; margin-bottom: 1rem; letter-spacing: 0.1em; text-transform: uppercase;">Legal</div>
      <h1 style="font-size: 2rem; font-weight: 900; color: #e2e8f0; margin: 0 0 1rem; letter-spacing: -0.02em;">Cookie Policy</h1>
      <p style="color: #4a5568; font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace; font-size: 0.8rem;">Last updated: 4 July 2026</p>
    </header>

    <div style="color: #a0aec0; line-height: 1.75; font-size: 0.95rem;">

      <section style="margin-bottom: 2.5rem;">
        <h2 style="font-size: 1.2rem; font-weight: 700; color: #e2e8f0; margin: 0 0 1rem;">What are cookies?</h2>
        <p>Cookies are small text files stored in your browser. This site uses localStorage (similar to cookies) to remember your preferences. We do not use any third-party tracking cookies.</p>
      </section>

      <section style="margin-bottom: 2.5rem;">
        <h2 style="font-size: 1.2rem; font-weight: 700; color: #e2e8f0; margin: 0 0 1rem;">Cookies we use</h2>

        <div style="border: 1px solid #1e1e2e; border-radius: 8px; overflow-x: auto; margin-top: 1rem;">
          <table style="width: 100%; min-width: 480px; border-collapse: collapse; font-size: 0.875rem; table-layout: fixed;">
            <thead>
              <tr style="background: #0a0a0f; border-bottom: 1px solid #1e1e2e;">
                <th style="text-align: left; padding: 0.75rem 1rem; color: #4a5568; font-size: 0.75rem; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.08em; width: 22%;">Name</th>
                <th style="text-align: left; padding: 0.75rem 1rem; color: #4a5568; font-size: 0.75rem; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.08em; width: 16%;">Type</th>
                <th style="text-align: left; padding: 0.75rem 1rem; color: #4a5568; font-size: 0.75rem; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.08em; width: 38%;">Purpose</th>
                <th style="text-align: left; padding: 0.75rem 1rem; color: #4a5568; font-size: 0.75rem; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.08em; width: 24%;">Expiry</th>
              </tr>
            </thead>
            <tbody>
              <tr style="border-bottom: 1px solid #1e1e2e; background: #111118;">
                <td style="padding: 0.75rem 1rem; color: #00d97e; font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace; font-size: 0.8rem; word-break: break-word;">cookie-accepted</td>
                <td style="padding: 0.75rem 1rem; color: #e2e8f0; font-size: 0.85rem; word-break: break-word;">Essential</td>
                <td style="padding: 0.75rem 1rem; color: #718096; word-break: break-word;">Remembers that you acknowledged the cookie notice</td>
                <td style="padding: 0.75rem 1rem; color: #718096; font-size: 0.85rem; word-break: break-word;">Persistent (localStorage)</td>
              </tr>
            </tbody>
          </table>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section style="margin-bottom: 2.5rem;">
        <h2 style="font-size: 1.2rem; font-weight: 700; color: #e2e8f0; margin: 0 0 1rem;">Analytics</h2>
        <p>We currently do not use any analytics service. If we add analytics in the future (e.g., Plausible Analytics — a privacy-friendly, GDPR-compliant tool), this policy will be updated and you will be given the option to opt out.</p>
      </section>

      <section style="margin-bottom: 2.5rem;">
        <h2 style="font-size: 1.2rem; font-weight: 700; color: #e2e8f0; margin: 0 0 1rem;">Third-party embeds</h2>
        <p>When you click a purchase link and are redirected to <a href="https://polar.sh" target="_blank" rel="noopener" style="color: #00d97e; text-decoration: none;">polar.sh</a>, their checkout page may set its own cookies. These are governed by <a href="https://polar.sh/legal/privacy" target="_blank" rel="noopener" style="color: #00d97e; text-decoration: none;">polar.sh's Privacy Policy</a>. We do not embed polar.sh iframes on this site.</p>
      </section>

      <section style="margin-bottom: 2.5rem;">
        <h2 style="font-size: 1.2rem; font-weight: 700; color: #e2e8f0; margin: 0 0 1rem;">How to clear cookies / localStorage</h2>
        <p>To clear the cookie notice setting, open your browser's developer tools, go to Application &rarr; Local Storage &rarr; missionctl.sh, and delete the <code style="font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace; background: #111118; padding: 0.1em 0.4em; border-radius: 3px; color: #00d97e;">cookie-accepted</code> entry.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 style="font-size: 1.2rem; font-weight: 700; color: #e2e8f0; margin: 0 0 1rem;">Contact</h2>
        <p>Questions about cookies? Email <a href="mailto:contact@missionctl.sh" style="color: #00d97e; text-decoration: none;">contact@missionctl.sh</a></p>
      </section>

    </div>
  </article>
</Layout>
